# BMSCE AI Chatbot

## Project Description
This project is an AI-powered chatbot designed to answer questions related to BMS College of Engineering.

The chatbot allows students and visitors to ask questions about courses, hostel facilities, and other college information.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Streamlit
- Groq API
- Llama 3.1
- FAISS Vector Database
- Sentence Transformers

## How It Works
1. User enters a question
2. Question is converted into embeddings
3. FAISS searches similar information
4. Context is sent to Llama 3.1 via Groq API
5. AI generates the final answer

